      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\nPedro S\xE1nchez V\xE1zquez.\n\nThis game is part of my TFG project
    in Universitat Oberta de Catalunya for my degree on Computer Science and Engineering.
    \n\nThe original game mechanics were taken from Azul boardgame by Kiesling M.
    \n\nArt: \nMost art in the game was AI generated using Nano Banana 2.  \n\nAlpha
    Testers:\n\nRub\xE9n Mart\xEDnez\nHuang Ming (Juan Miguel Cespedes Naveros)\nJuegos
    N\xF3madas\nNuma84\n\nMusic:\nMenu: Stay by my side - Rodrigo Flores\nGame: Fields
    of Grain Piano - Jacob Lives\n\nDevelopement:\nPedro S\xE1nchez V\xE1zquez\n2026\n\nDisclaimer:
    I respect the work of the wonderful artists that create inmersive and liveful
    gaming experiences. However, given my time restrictions and available resources
    as a student  I opted for AI as a source of quick prototype images for the game.\n\nThanks
    for playing.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n"
